description: This script provides a command-line utility to connect via Telnet to a device, fetch an rx-signal value, and output the information in JSON format. It manages environment variables for configuration and utilizes the server.py module's TelnetClient and iso_now functions.

methods.name: main()
methods.description: Main function that reads environment variables, establishes a Telnet connection, fetches rx-signal data, and outputs results as JSON.
